        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figs 195–202. Arganthomyza socculata (Zetterstedt, 1847), female (USA: Alaska). 195 – postabdomen, dorsally; 196 – spermatheca; 197 – internal sclerites and apex of postabdomen, laterally; 198 – internal sclerites, ventrally; 199 – distal part of female genital chamber,laterally; 200 – spermatheca; 201 – postabdomen, ventrally; 202 – ventral receptacle, laterally. Scales = 0.2 mm (Figs 195, 201), 0.1 mm (Figs 197–199) and 0.05 mm (others).Adapted from ROHÁĆEK & BARBER (2013: Figs 152–159)." ;
